title: The Jungle Book
subTitle: Mowgli, who is raised by Akela's wolf pack, goes on daily adventures with his friends, Baloo and Bagheera. He tries to help many animals who are in danger.

title: Rainbow Rangers
subTitle: Seven young girls strive hard to protect the citizens of a magical land, Kaleidoscopia. Subsequently, with the help of their superpowers, they try to make the world a better place.

title: Thomas Edison's Secret Lab
subTitle: After discovering Thomas Edison's secret laboratory, Angie and his friends enter the world of science and unravel various phenomena with the help of Edison's ghost.

subTitle: After losing his powers in a fight with his arch nemesis, Captain Fantastic now works undercover as a kindergarten teacher. Here he must help train a new generation of superpowered children.
